-Run the Cube Mapping Tool processing script and place the cubes in their desired position
-Any cubes at the origin will be ignored
-Click Save
-A text file with the mapping coordinates will be automatically created in the directory called mappingfile.txt





-using terminal CD into the SLSStudio directory
and run the mapping script by typing:
perl tools/mapping_tool_parser.pl

-before hitting enter hit space and drag the mappingfile.txt into terminal (located in the cube mapping tool directory)

-hit enter

-Enjoy